Now i am wondering if i should do another week or two and be more organised on psmf or do a 15-1800 calorie diet for the next few weeks orrrr just do a typical 2100 diet for another 10 weeks.. My personal tips, get ENOUGH sleep !! Meal prep even if its in the morning for the evening. intermittent Fast, try and do OMAD too or within a short window like 2-3 hours. Make your food interesting, psmf isnt even that bad if you know how to cook.
